<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>317</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 tā ràng wǒ men huó dào jīn tiān, wǒ men tóng shēng lái gǎn xiè tā,
 tā ràng wǒ men huó dào jīn tiān, wǒ men dōu yào róng yào tā,
 hái yǒu yī chéng, hái yǒu yī chéng, hái yǒu yī chéng jiù dǐ dá tiān jiā.
 hái yǒu yī chéng, hái yǒu yī chéng nǐ ná shén me qù jiàn tā.</lyrics>
<title>hái yǒu yī chéng 迦南317</title>
</song>